  66:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c **** 
  67:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****     [..]
  68:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****      The compilation flag USE_HAL_SUBGHZ_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
  69:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****      allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
  70:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****      Use Functions @ref HAL_SUBGHZ_RegisterCallback() or @ref HAL_SUBGHZ_RegisterAddrCallback()
  71:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****      to register an interrupt callback.
  72:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c **** 
  73:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****     [..]
  74:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****      Function @ref HAL_SUBGHZ_RegisterCallback() allows to register following callbacks:
  75:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) TxCpltCallback           : callback for Tx Completed.
  76:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) RxCpltCallback           : callback for Rx Completed.
  77:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) PreambleDetectedCallback : callback for Preamble detected.
  78:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) SyncWordValidCallback    : callback for Synchro word valid.
  79:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) HeaderValidCallback      : callback for Header valid.
  80:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) HeaderErrorCallback      : callback for Header error.
  81:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) CRCErrorCallback         : callback for CRC Error.
  82:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) RxTxTimeoutCallback      : callback for Rx Tx Timeout.
  83:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) MspInitCallback          : callback for Msp Init.
  84:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) MspDeInitCallback        : callback for Msp DeInit.
  85:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****        (+) LrFhssHopCallback        : callback for LoRa Frequency Hopping Spread Spectrum Hopping.
  86:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****      This function takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle, the Callback ID
  87:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****      and a pointer to the user callback function.
  88:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_subghz.c ****     [..]
